OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy but dry start, with
OL,6,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,7,Fmorning, the best of these in the
OL,8,Feast. Chance of a few spots of rain
OL,9,Ffurther west later. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy overnight and dry,
OL,12,Fwith some occasional breaks in the
OL,13,Fcloud, temperatures will fall but
OL,14,Fremain above freezing. Winds becoming
OL,15,Flight and variable.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FAfter a cool start, Tuesday
OL,18,Fwill be dry with light winds. Cloudy
OL,19,Ffor the most with some occasional
OL,20,Fsunny spells during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
